## Rating Field

A numeric rating field rendered as a row of star icons; the max value, icon, and read-only state are configurable.

### Usage

```ts
import { CardDef, field, contains } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';
import RatingField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/rating/rating';

export class Example extends CardDef {
  @field score = contains(RatingField, {
    configuration: { maxRating: 5 },
  });
}
```

See the **Examples** section of this spec for the full set of supported configuration options.
